title: VisEraseNet
description: VisEraseNet introduces a multimodal deep learning framework that intelligently detects, segments, and removes unwanted logos, texts, and objects from images and videos — achieving high-quality, context-aware restorations without artifacts.

title: Project RoboCam
description: RoboCam is an advanced robotic surevillance system designed for automation and security. It integrates AI and robotics to perform surveillance, threat detection, and response, ensuring enhanced safety and efficiency in various environments.

title: Murphy Systum
description: A comprehensive Medical Diagnosis System that includes multiple disease detection modules using Machine Learning and Deep Learning models. The system currently supports: ✅ Brain Tumor Detection ✅ Breast Cancer Classification ✅ General Disease Prediction based on symptoms

title: Cell Center Performance
description: This project analyzes call center performance using real-world data to identify key metrics and showcases the application of data analysis in a service-oriented environment using tool like Power BI.

title: Revenue Insights of Hospital Domain
description: This project explores financial data from the healthcare sector to uncover trends and patterns in hospital revenue. The focus is on deriving insights that support profitability and efficiency within hospitals, using tools like Power BI.
